{{Top|leg}}
A '''hypo''' was a medical tool that was used to administer drugs such as [[Truth serum/Legends|truth serum]]s<ref name="CCG-Hypo">{{CCG|set=A New Hope Limited|cardname=Hypo}}</ref> and sedatives. A hypo was used to administer a strong sedative to the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Lorana Jinzler]] after she was kidnapped by [[Brolf]]i terrorists.<ref name="Outbound Flight">[[Outbound Flight (novel)|''Outbound Flight'']]</ref>

The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] also used a hypo, mounted on an [[IT-O interrogation droid/Legends|IT-O interrogation droid]], to administer the truth serum [[Bavo Six]]<ref name="CCG-Hypo" /> during the interrogation of [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] on the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|first Death Star]], in an attempt to gain the location of the [[Great Temple/Legends|hidden Rebel base]] from her.<ref name="ANH">{{Film|IV}}</ref>

